<div class="anchor-list">
<a name="1" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub43291_1" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="节目历史" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">走近科学</span>节目历史</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="1" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="anchor-list">
<a name="1_1" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub43291_1_1" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="节目背景" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="1-1" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">走近科学</span>节目背景</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">科普类电视节目随着“科教兴国”政策的实施和第一部科普法的颁布，受到各级媒体的重视，并且伴随中央电视台科教频道和一些专业的科技电视栏目的开播，取得了很好的社会反响。在电视荧屏上呈现出更多的是精品电视节目。但是，这类电视节目似乎很难在普及科学技术知识与达到最佳效果之间寻找到一个平衡点，达到一个知识性、思想性、艺术性、观赏性兼备的目标。《走近科学》就在这个背景下，作为一个带领人们认识科学的栏目应运而生。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="2" data-ctrmap=":2,">
[2]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[2]_43291">&nbsp;</a>
</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="1_2" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub43291_1_2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="发展历程" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="1-2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">走近科学</span>发展历程</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><a class="lemma-album layout-right nslog:10000206" title="走近科学历年片头"  href="/pic/%E8%B5%B0%E8%BF%91%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/793933/22536189/0df3d7ca7bcb0a463b1ed13f6063f6246b60affc?fr=lemma&ct=cover" target="_blank"  style="width:222px;" nslog-type="10000206">
<div class="album-wrap" style="width:220px;height:155px;">
<img class="picture" alt="走近科学历年片头" src="https://gss1.bdstatic.com/9vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=42d5dc2a8c01a18bf4eb154dae2f0761/0df3d7ca7bcb0a463b1ed13f6063f6246b60affc.jpg" style="width:220px;height:155px;"/>
</div>
<div class="description">
走近科学历年片头<span class="number">(5张)</span>
</div>
<div class="albumBg">
<div class="albumBgFir" style="width:214px;"></div>
<div class="albumBgSec" style="width:208px;"></div>
</div>
</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">1995年，“科教兴国”战略提出，广电部组织召开专家座谈会，研讨广播电视行业如何为“科教兴国”战略服务。电视成为进行科教宣传的重要手段。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="3" data-ctrmap=":3,">
[3]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[3]_43291">&nbsp;</a>
<a name="ref_3"></a><a name="ref_3"></a><a name="ref_3"></a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">1998年6月1日，日播科教节目《走近科学》栏目成立，并在央视一套播出。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">2001年7月9日，《走近科学》改由中央电视台科教频道播出，同时节目形式从追求涵盖面广的板块式结构变为了每期一个主题的通篇结构。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="3" data-ctrmap=":3,">
[3]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[3]_43291">&nbsp;</a>
<a name="ref_3"></a><a name="ref_3"></a><a name="ref_3"></a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">2003年，《走近科学》因为收视率不佳而受到了黄牌警告，栏目的生存一度受到威胁。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="3" data-ctrmap=":3,">
[3]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[3]_43291">&nbsp;</a>
<a name="ref_3"></a><a name="ref_3"></a><a name="ref_3"></a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">2004年3月，节目表现形式从报道科学问题，解释科学事件转变为：关注和报道生活中的推理故事；热点、疑点的科学解析。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="3" data-ctrmap=":3,">
[3]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[3]_43291">&nbsp;</a>
<a name="ref_3"></a><a name="ref_3"></a><a name="ref_3"></a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">2019年9月30日，走近科学播出最后一期节目。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="4" data-ctrmap=":4,">
[4]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[4]_43291">&nbsp;</a>
</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="2" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub43291_2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="节目形式" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">走近科学</span>节目形式</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="2" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="anchor-list">
<a name="2_1" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub43291_2_1" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="节目制作" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="2-1" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">走近科学</span>节目制作</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; cursor: move; text-indent: 28px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E8%B5%B0%E8%BF%91%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/793933/0/c8ea15ce36d3d539113293403087e950352ab022?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="《走近科学》节目图片" style="width:220px;height:168px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss3.bdstatic.com/7Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=b6ed005f8013632711edc531a18ea056/c8ea15ce36d3d539113293403087e950352ab022.jpg"  alt="《走近科学》节目图片" style="width:220px;height:168px;"/>
</a>
<span class="description">
《走近科学》节目图片
</span>
</div></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">节目利用科教知识的专业性与大众化相融合，尽可能多的接触不同阶层的受众，用大众化的语言，故事化的表现方式，曲折的情节进行传播。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="5" data-ctrmap=":5,">
[5]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[5]_43291">&nbsp;</a>
<a name="ref_5"></a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">节目通过影像和音响元素增加紧张感，渲染悬疑的气氛，引爆观众的好奇心。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="6" data-ctrmap=":6,">
[6]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[6]_43291">&nbsp;</a>
<a name="ref_6"></a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">节目通过讲述科研过程中的曲折故事，展示科学的无限魅力以及科学家们献身科研的感人事迹，让观众在了解科学知识的同时也感受到科学家的人格魅力。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="1" data-ctrmap=":1,">
[1]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[1]_43291">&nbsp;</a>
<a name="ref_1"></a><a name="ref_1"></a><a name="ref_1"></a></div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="2_2" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub43291_2_2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="节目特色" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="2-2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">走近科学</span>节目特色</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">节目的主题涉及社会生活的方方面面，既有专业的科学知识，以讲故事的形式同时告诉观众一个科学原理，同时又有生活中遇到的难以解决的问题和不同寻常的现象，还有自然环境和地理形势的科学探索，包含面比较广泛。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="5" data-ctrmap=":5,">
[5]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[5]_43291">&nbsp;</a>
<a name="ref_5"></a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">节目的视线不仅停留在科技前沿的热门话题．而且也关注各个科研领域的最新进展。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="1" data-ctrmap=":1,">
[1]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[1]_43291">&nbsp;</a>
<a name="ref_1"></a><a name="ref_1"></a><a name="ref_1"></a></div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="2_3" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub43291_2_3" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="节目环节" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="2-3" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">走近科学</span>节目环节</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; cursor: move; text-indent: 28px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E8%B5%B0%E8%BF%91%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/793933/0/e850352ac65c1038852c7a41b8119313b17e89e7?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="走近科学" style="width:220px;height:169px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/-fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=768389495b3d26972ad30f5f65fab24f/e850352ac65c1038852c7a41b8119313b17e89e7.jpg"  alt="走近科学" style="width:220px;height:169px;"/>
</a>
<span class="description">
走近科学
</span>
</div>节目主要由生活中的各种与众不同的现象引发的各类传奇的经历和故事，用悬念、矛盾和冲突来构架故事情节，采用情景回放和主持人串联的方式，关注当事人和事件的发展，栏目将科学知识融入到生活中。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="1" data-ctrmap=":1,">
[1]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[1]_43291">&nbsp;</a>
<a name="ref_1"></a><a name="ref_1"></a><a name="ref_1"></a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">节目运用灵活多样的表现手法，在节目表现上将科学现象故事化、情节化，通过科幻视角的切入，设置悬疑，层层推进，调动起受众的好奇心。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="6" data-ctrmap=":6,">
[6]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[6]_43291">&nbsp;</a>
<a name="ref_6"></a></div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="3" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub43291_3" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="创作团队" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
